==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sea girdles
<hw>Sea" gir"dles</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A kind of
kelp (<spn>Laminaria digitata</spn>) with palmately cleft fronds; --
called also <altname>sea wand</altname>, <altname>seaware</altname>, and
<xex>tangle</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Seagirt</ent>⟦br⟧
